                            <li>Yoga sessions.</li>
                            <li>As south India is famous in Ayurvedic Messages. Spa Facilities.</li>
                            <li>Swimming pool.</li>
                            <li>Very important Gym area.</li>
                            <li>Gaming section.</li>
                        </ol>
                        <p>
                            They can have there own mode of relaxation choices. These all things help traveler to enjoy travelling and waiting area will be more fun than boring. Moreover they carry the most beautiful experiences and like to travel again.                            .
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-4">
                        <h4>Facilities Available</h4><hr>
                        <div class="divide10"></div>
                        <div class="services-2">
